%o A002081 (PARI) a(n) = 5*n + [2,-1,-2,1][(n%4)+1] \\ _Ralf Stephan_, Jun 08 2005
%o A002081 (PARI) is(n) = n > 0 && setsearch([2,4,8,16], n%20) > 0 \\ _Rick L. Shepherd_, Aug 17 2016
